reviewText: I've seen better cartoons, and these are not them. I don't remember these cartoons being this boring. Dont get me wrong, there OK, but...Bugs Bunny has nothing to worry about
Great movies, fun characters, good storys worth getting thanks. P.S. time kid is the movie instead of 20000 lengths under the sea movie on the box
good collection of cartoons. this dvd is fun and enjoyable to watch if you have not seen this dvd then i recommend you do
These cartoons bring back such childhood memories.

I recieved the item! but the problem is it didn't have the disc inside. I don't know if it was a manufacture problem or what not, but i was very disappointmented. Because out of all of the disc i recieved today, this is the one that i was really looking forward to looking at.

Even though im in my early 40"s watching these cartoons just bring back the old days.
It is great to see simple cartoons again.
This DVD is great and funny too.
